import { v4 as uuidv4 } from 'uuid';

var initialState =[
    {
        id:uuidv4(),
        name: "iPhone 13 pro max",
        image1:"",

        price:1000,
        dscription:"",
        inventory:33,
        rating: 5

    {
        id:uuidv4(),
        name: "iPhone XS max",
        image1:"",
        image2: "",
        price:900,
        dscription:"",
        inventory:33,
        rating: 3

    {

        name: "iPad Pro M1",

        price:1500,
        dscription:"",
        inventory:33,

    {

        image1:"",

        price:3000,
        dscription:"",
        inventory:13,
        rating: 5

    {

        name: "iPhone 12 pro max",
        image1:"",
        image2: "",
        price:1000,
        dscription:"",
        inventory:33,
        rating: 5

]

const products = (state = initialState, action) => {
    switch(action.type){
        default : return [...state]
    }
}
export default products;
